cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language grounding in images. It is also likely to belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) because it involves visual grounding. Additionally, it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because it involves developing a novel modular network for reasoning. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) because it involves training the network end-to-end using the Gumbel-Softmax approximation and its straight-through gradient estimator.
